column5: As the title says, I am looking for Lady Evelyn reports. I am leaving next saturday to spend a week fishing and camping there. Just wondering how the fishing has been and what the water level is at.  Thanks Mark

Hey Mark, There are 8 of us heading up there in September, and we've been keeping in contact with the lodge owner about water levels. According to out last update, Friday, the water levels are good. That's all I can help with, but it's better than nothin'.
Thanks for the reply. That is good news about the water level. I will post a report when I get back.  Mark
